'Glen Waverley police are hoping that love is not lost – even though the ring appears to be,' a spokesperson wrote in a media release aimed at hunting down the former-wearer.

'The ring is silver with a single diamond and appears to be a man's wedding ring judging by the size.'

Social media users responded by predicting how the ring ended up in the field and what consequences the owner might face when discovered by the mysterious Julie.

