'Coming soon: "Glen Waverly male found assaulted for losing wedding ring. Police wish to speak with Julie",' Michael Jon Ovcaric commented on the post.

'She probably cheated on him so he threw it out... Or he could of been drunk and threw it out the window?' Pasi Julian Levae guessed.

Victoria police are asking anyone who believes they own the ring or knows who it might belong to to call Glen Waverley police station on 9566 1555. 

